extends layout

block content
  .page-header
    h1.page-title Our Services
    p.page-subtitle Comprehensive solutions for your business needs
  
  .content-section
    .container
      .services-grid
        .service-card
          .service-icon
            span 💼
          h3 Business Consulting
          p Strategic planning and business development services to help your company grow and succeed in today's competitive market.
          ul
            li Market analysis and research
            li Strategic planning and implementation
            li Process optimization
            li Performance improvement
        
        .service-card
          .service-icon
            span 💻
          h3 Technology Solutions
          p Cutting-edge technology services designed to streamline your operations and enhance productivity.
          ul
            li Software development and integration
            li IT infrastructure management
            li Digital transformation consulting
            li Technical support and maintenance
        
        .service-card
          .service-icon
            span 📊
          h3 Financial Services
          p Professional financial guidance and services to help manage your business finances effectively.
          ul
            li Financial planning and analysis
            li Accounting and bookkeeping
            li Tax preparation and compliance
            li Investment advisory services
        
        .service-card
          .service-icon
            span 🎯
          h3 Marketing & Sales
          p Comprehensive marketing strategies to boost your brand visibility and drive sales growth.
          ul
            li Digital marketing campaigns
            li Brand development and positioning
            li Sales strategy and training
            li Customer relationship management
  
  .cta-section
    .container
      h2 Interested in Our Services?
      p Contact us during business hours to discuss your specific requirements and get a customized quote.
      .business-hours
        p 📅 Monday to Friday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM
      a.btn.btn-primary(href='/contact') Request a Quote
